{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":588630,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你还真以为他一辈子不会在恋爱了啊？","timestamp":1605865863,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":588642,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我小时候说过好几次一辈子不会再玩游戏了","timestamp":1605866086,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":588651,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"高中啊喂，忘了吧，不至于","timestamp":1605866167,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":588674,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"那句话，也许只是代表，他当时的心情与感受。他想传达给你的，也许只是他当时很痛苦，还有对爱情幻想的破灭。不管他此时此刻如何，其实不必在乎，只要当时你俩真感情对待过彼此就够了。有人活在过去，也有人不停向前，人生的选择是多样的。哀吾生之须臾，羡长江之无穷，活在当下，勇敢向前，难道不应该为他开心嘛。如果他因和你分手，惶惶不可终日，于是变成一个废人，这会是你希望看到的吗。曾经彼此拥有过，一起享受快乐的时光就足够了。","timestamp":1605866420,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":588687,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: ？璀璨？","timestamp":1605866522,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":588688,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"？","timestamp":1605866524,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":588754,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我高中时候喜欢一个同班的女孩，因为喜欢她，选择学文，想和她在一个班。三年，最终爷也没表白过。因为后来才知道她有男朋友。大一时候，她和前男友分手，我高兴了很长时间，觉得自己有戏了，后来她又找了一个，当时难受的要死，后来也就没啥感觉了。","timestamp":1605867107,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":588761,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你现在是还喜欢你前男友吗？","timestamp":1605867191,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":591901,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: 并不，单纯觉得有点好笑","timestamp":1605898748,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":591908,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: Grace不表白也太可惜了","timestamp":1605898806,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":591912,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 当时当然是不信的，很诧异。但说完这句话几个月不到进入大学就也属实有趣","timestamp":1605898882,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":591914,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 有道理","timestamp":1605898891,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":591916,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 确实，我有喜欢男生了。发这个只是心里还是有些五味杂陈吧","timestamp":1605898917,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":591919,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122415,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: Dave说的太对了，属实感动呜呜呜。言语不能表达我对您的膜","timestamp":1605898972,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":7,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":122415,"reply":14,"tag":null,"text":"前男友跟我分手时说自己一辈子不会再恋爱了（初一相恋，异地到高中毕业，暑假分手）\n去了不同的大学\n我来了我清他待在四川\n现在看他跟他女朋友QQ名片和空间里秀来秀去\n感觉不能再好笑","timestamp":1605865820,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782653,"url":"","vote":{}}}